
-------- Battle Rhythm Game --------

This project is started as a HSC Major Work but is intnded to continue as an open source project.

The core of this project is a 4 track rhythm game. From left to right the notes are scored with Q, W, O and P when they are within the scoring area.

Instant rhythm mode allows the player to quickly choose a song and begin playing any of the game's songs with their selection of mechanics.

In challenge mode players attempt to complete rhythms with set goals and mechanics.

- Instant rhythm mechanic selection is not yet implemented.
- Challenge mode is not yet implemented.

- Mechnics to implement;
	reload

Language is Python 3.3 and uses the pygame library

